data.description: Welcome to your new home in Penrose! On over an acre of land, this charming home has four bedrooms and three bathrooms. The oversized living room has plenty of space for furniture and entertaining. The kitchen and dining room have plenty of cabinets and counter space as well. This property also includes an attached two-car garage, as well as a shed for additional storage. This home provides easy access to nearby amenities, less than half a mile away from two local restaurants and State Highway 115.
